text.tspan: A: Submit signup form with valid Stripe token
D: Establish wormhole for new active subscription
E: Respond with signup success page (including wormhole code)
G: Respond with active subscriptions (including new active subscription)
H: Create subscription ConfigMap, Deployment, etc
I: Copy wormhole code (from E) to invite dialog
J: Attempt wormhole connect (with wormhole code from success page - D)
K{1,2}: Convey subscription details via wormhole
